[2] Global update: Polio Eradication Initiative
Date: Wed 5 Mar 2014
Source: The Global Polio Eradication Initiative (GPEI) [edited]
http://polioeradication.org/Dataandmonitoring/Poliothisweek.aspx


Global Polio Eradication Initiative update as of 5 Mar 2014
